<% layout('layout') -%>
<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-content">
<section class="rules-section">
  <h2>The Claryville Open — Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

  <h3>What We Collect</h3>
  <p>When you register for the tournament, we collect your name, email address, phone number, age, and gender. When you subscribe to our mailing list, we collect your email address. When you text our SMS chatbot, we process your phone number and message content.</p>

  <h3>How We Use It</h3>
  <ul class="rules-list">
    <li>To manage tournament registration and group assignments</li>
    <li>To send tournament-related emails (confirmations, updates, results)</li>
    <li>To respond to your questions via our SMS chatbot or email</li>
    <li>To calculate team handicap strokes and tee box assignments</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>SMS/Text Messaging</h3>
  <ul class="rules-list">
    <li>When you text our number (1-833-HSQ-OPEN), you consent to receive automated SMS replies to your questions</li>
    <li>Message and data rates may apply</li>
    <li>Message frequency varies based on your questions</li>
    <li>Text <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to opt out</li>
    <li>Text <strong>HELP</strong> for support information</li>
    <li>We do not send marketing messages via SMS</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Sharing</h3>
  <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties. Your data is only used for tournament operations. We use third-party services (Cloudflare, Telnyx, Resend, Stripe) to operate the website, email, SMS, and donations — each governed by their own privacy policies.</p>

  <h3>Data Retention</h3>
  <p>Registration data is retained for the current tournament year and historical records. You can request deletion of your data by emailing <a href="mailto:admin@claryvilleopen.com">admin@claryvilleopen.com</a>.</p>

  <h3>Contact</h3>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:admin@claryvilleopen.com">admin@claryvilleopen.com</a>.</p>
</section>
</div>
